# Each workspace owns its own .env. This file is a pointer.
#
# apps/web/.env       -> Vite reads VITE_* vars from here
#                        See apps/web/.env.example
#
# apps/api/.env       -> Fastify reads DATABASE_URL, SUPABASE_JWT_SECRET, etc.
#                        See apps/api/.env.example
#
# Do not put secrets at the repo root.
